package io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.mod.registration
Classes for the LibX registration system. See ModXRegistration for more information.

    RegistryCondition
    A registry condition is used by the LibX registration system to prevent things passed to ModXRegistration.register(String, Object) from being registered.
    RegistryTransformer
    A registry transformer is used by the LibX registration system to register additional things dynamically based on other objects, that have been passed to the system.
